; Global definitions - put at the top of the colorscheme {{{
Terminal             -> Normal
StatusLineTerm       -> StatusLine
StatusLineTermNC     -> StatusLineNC
MessageWindow        -> Pmenu
PopupNotification    -> Todo
Boolean              -> Constant
Character            -> Constant
Conditional          -> Statement
Define               -> PreProc
Debug                -> Special
Delimiter            -> Special
ErrorMsg             -> Error
Exception            -> Statement
Float                -> Constant
Function             -> Identifier
Include              -> PreProc
Keyword              -> Statement
Label                -> Statement
Macro                -> PreProc
Number               -> Constant
Operator             -> Statement
PreCondit            -> PreProc
Repeat               -> Statement
SpecialChar          -> Special
SpecialComment       -> Special
StorageClass         -> Type
Structure            -> Type
Tag                  -> Special
Typedef              -> Type
; See `:help lCursor`
lCursor              -> Cursor
; Custom
debugPC              -> CursorLine
; }}}

